Hello! My name is Sarah, and I am representing RT 6 Boozers. How can I assist you today?

Hi Sarah! I'm looking for some information about your happy hour specials.

Of course! We have a great happy hour that runs from four PM to six PM every weekday. What's your name so I can personalize our conversation?

My name is Alex.

Thank you, Alex! I appreciate it. Could I also have your email address so I can send you details about our promotions?

Sure! It's alex.jones at example dot com.

Great! And just one more thing, could you provide me with your birth year?

I was born in nineteen ninety.

Thank you for sharing that, Alex! You will be eligible for our birthday special when that time comes.

That sounds awesome! I'm looking forward to it.

Thank you for your time, Alex! If you have any more questions, feel free to ask. Have a wonderful day!
